## Every button — exact behavior

| Button | Where | What it does |
|---|---|---|
| `+ Add root category` | top right | opens `CategoryModal` with `parentId=null`, `level=0` |
| `Edit` | any row | opens `CategoryModal` pre-filled with that category's data |
| `+ Sub` | root or sub row | sets `inlineParentId` → renders `InlineAddForm` inline below the row; only one can be open at a time |
| `Del` | any row | opens `DeleteConfirm` modal → on confirm: `DELETE` cascade via FK, refetch |
| `Save` (inline form) | inline form | `INSERT` with `parent_id`, auto-computed `level`, auto-generated `slug`, then refetch + close form |
| `Cancel` (inline form) | inline form | clears `inlineParentId`, collapses form |
| `Save` (modal) | modal | `UPSERT` — if `id` exists → `UPDATE`, else `INSERT`; if `parent_id` changed → recompute `slug` and `level`; refetch |
| `⠿` drag handle | any row | drag-and-drop sort within same parent group → batch `UPDATE sort_order` |
| Status dot / badge | any row | clicking toggles `is_active` inline via optimistic update |
| Row expand toggle `+` | rows with children | toggles `expandedIds` — children render/hide |

