## UX rules to enforce

- Only **one inline form** open at a time — opening a new +Sub closes the previous one.
- Slug is **auto-generated but editable** in the modal only. Inline form never shows slug field.
- **Optimistic update** for toggle active/inactive — flip locally, rollback on error.
- **Delete** always requires a confirm dialog showing: `"Delete [name]? This will also delete [n] sub-categories and unlink [n] products."`
- Drag-to-sort is **within the same parent group only** — you can't drag a sub under a different root by dragging in this table (that's a "Move" via the modal's parent dropdown).
- The **"Move" action** lives inside the Edit modal as a parent dropdown — changing it recomputes slug and level on save.